# INSTALLATION GUIDE

1) Install Archipelago at https://github.com/ArchipelagoMW/Archipelago/releases/tag/0.6.7
Installation Guide https://archipelago.gg/tutorial/Archipelago/setup_en

2) Install manual_skylandersspyrosadventurewi_ver1.apworld in Archipelago client
-Open ArchipelagoLauncher.exe
-Locate "install APworld and press "Open"
-Navigate to manual_skylandersspyrosadventurewi_ver1.apworld
-This will take a moment, and will confirm with a textbox once installed

3) Create Game
-Edit Manual_SkylandersSpyrosAdventureWi_ver1.yaml (open in text editor) and change the "name" to your dessired slot name (Defaults to Player(Number)
-Copy this file to Archipelago > Players 
(If you wish to play with other games or friends, also install all .apworld files, then gather their .yaml files and place them in this folder)
-In Archipelago Launcher, locate "Generate"  and press "Open". If succeessful, this will create a folder in Archipelago > Output. Upload this to https://archipelago.gg/uploads or under local host option in the launcher

4) Open Client
-In Archipelago Launcher, locate "Manual Client" and press open
-Connect the client to the server your seeed is beeing hosted at. On the website, the room provides a /connect command that can be pasted, or use /connect [IP]
-Enter your slot name, which you specified in the .yaml
-At the top, select the "Manual" tab. This will display all currently obtained items and all locations to check


A) Gather Skylanders Collection. This Randomiser requires all 32 standard skylanders and non-adventure pack magic items. These may be reset or pre-preepareed, as per player preference

B) Create required save file
-Save File requires all 26 chapters to be complete with NO 3RD-STAR COLLECTABLES OR WINGED SAPPHIRES COLLECTED
-For Dolphin Players, a copy of a valid savefile is included in the download. 
-To install on dolphin, set the folder containing your Spyro's Adventure ISO as dolphin's default. Then right click, press "Open Wii Savee Folder" and paste aa copy of this savedile into this folder
-For console, create this savefile, export it to SD Card, and keep a backup somewhere safe
# UNLESS YOU ARE CONFIDENT WITH SSA'S COLLECTABLES, IT IS RECOMMENDED YOU KEEP A BACKUP COPY OF THE REQUIRED SAVE FILE AND LOAD IT WHEN YOU PLAY A NEW SEED
